               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18481023-name-1066" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18481023-name-1066" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18481023-name-1066" type="surname" value="CLARK"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18481023-name-1066" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM CLARK</persName>
                  </hi>. I have a shop at Maryland Point, Stratford—it was broken open, and I lost some tools, on 14th Oct.—these are my tools.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. BALLANTINE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> What is the prisoner? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> A fellow-workman of mine—he had not the key of the shop—I left the tools safe on Saturday night, just after six o'clock, and the shop locked up—I left no one there.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18481023-name-1067" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18481023-name-1067" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18481023-name-1067" type="surname" value="PESZUKSKI"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18481023-name-1067" type="given" value="TITUS"></interp>TITUS PESZUKSKI</persName>
                  </hi>. I met the prisoner with some tools, on the Saturday night, at eight o'clock—he carried the plough under his arm—I said, "Have you finished your work?"—he said, "No"—I left him, and did not see him again till Monday morning—I told Clark.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18481023-name-1068" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18481023-name-1068" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18481023-name-1068" type="surname" value="POTTER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18481023-name-1068" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM POTTER</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, K</hi> 273). I went with Clark to the prisoner, and asked if he took away any tools, on Saturday night, from the shop—he said, "No"—I said, "You were met with some"—he denied carrying any away.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
