                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, K</hi> 381). I went with Potter to the pri<lb></lb>soner's lodging, at Maryland Point, and found this plough, saw, and some tools claimed by Philip Wilson—the prisoner told me where I should find the tools.</p>
